290
00:17:36,150 --> 00:17:36,780
Fu Ying.

291
00:17:37,670 --> 00:17:39,300
You haven't found Light Messenger?

292
00:17:39,470 --> 00:17:40,710
No, I contacted them.

293
00:17:40,733 --> 00:17:42,311
They're always out of the service area.

294
00:17:44,866 --> 00:17:45,844
It's time for lunch.

295
00:17:46,060 --> 00:17:46,710
Eat first.

296
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,190
I'm so busy that I forget.

297
00:17:49,190 --> 00:17:49,911
I'll go eat first.

298
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:51,300
Go ahead.

299
00:18:08,870 --> 00:18:11,300
The number you dialed is unanswered.

300
00:18:11,580 --> 00:18:13,060
Please call again later.

301
00:18:13,260 --> 00:18:13,740
Sorry.

302
00:18:13,870 --> 00:18:16,190
The number you dialed is unanswered.

303
00:18:30,580 --> 00:18:32,150
You finally picked up.

304
00:18:32,230 --> 00:18:33,888
What are you doing? Why did you keep...

305
00:18:38,470 --> 00:18:39,430
Are you in the hospital?

306
00:18:40,422 --> 00:18:41,630
You're not feeling well?

307
00:18:43,190 --> 00:18:44,670
My gastroenteritis has flared up.

308
00:18:44,933 --> 00:18:46,844
I feel much better
after getting an IV drip.

309
00:18:46,910 --> 00:18:47,910
Gastroenteritis?

310
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:50,000
Why did you suddenly
get gastroenteritis?

311
00:18:50,333 --> 00:18:52,311
Did you eat something
that upset your stomach?

312
00:18:53,390 --> 00:18:55,340
My stomach was upset yesterday.

313
00:18:55,555 --> 00:18:58,111
I thought I'd be fine
after a good night's sleep.

314
00:19:01,100 --> 00:19:02,630
Why didn't you tell me?

315
00:19:03,870 --> 00:19:05,820
I didn't think it was a big deal.

316
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:12,020
How are you feeling now?

317
00:19:15,822 --> 00:19:17,150
If I could be by your side...

318
00:19:17,230 --> 00:19:17,910
Huan'er.

319
00:19:24,377 --> 00:19:25,644
I just bought you some porridge.

320
00:19:25,666 --> 00:19:26,777
Eat it while it's hot.

321
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:27,630
Thank you.

322
00:19:28,470 --> 00:19:29,390
Tian Chi.

323
00:19:29,390 --> 00:19:30,990
I thought you left.

324
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:31,820
No.

325
00:19:34,540 --> 00:19:35,430
Was it Jing Xichi?

326
00:19:37,540 --> 00:19:38,060
Yes.

327
00:19:41,060 --> 00:19:41,990
Eat it while it's hot.

328
00:19:41,990 --> 00:19:43,750
Eating it
will make your stomach feel better.

329
00:19:43,755 --> 00:19:44,711
You can't faint again.

330
00:19:45,950 --> 00:19:46,950
Thank you, Tian Chi.

331
00:19:47,540 --> 00:19:49,100
I've troubled you enough today.

332
00:19:49,390 --> 00:19:50,820
You should go back and rest.

333
00:19:52,340 --> 00:19:52,780
Sure.

334
00:19:53,111 --> 00:19:54,488
You should rest early too.

335
00:19:55,100 --> 00:19:55,740
Thank you.

336
00:20:02,710 --> 00:20:03,990
You fainted?

337
00:20:06,780 --> 00:20:08,020
In the lab today.

338
00:20:08,230 --> 00:20:09,710
Tian Chi happened to see me

339
00:20:09,870 --> 00:20:10,950
and sent me to the hospital.

340
00:20:13,950 --> 00:20:15,390
Which hospital are you in?

341
00:20:15,488 --> 00:20:17,000
I'll ask Yan Mu to accompany you.

342
00:20:17,260 --> 00:20:18,060
No.

343
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:19,670
I can take care of myself.

344
00:20:19,950 --> 00:20:21,820
You should handle Yangwu's affairs.

345
00:20:25,060 --> 00:20:25,820
Rest

346
00:20:26,260 --> 00:20:27,150
a bit longer then.

347
00:20:27,911 --> 00:20:29,444
Call me if anything happens.

348
00:20:30,630 --> 00:20:31,150
Bye.

349
00:20:32,190 --> 00:20:32,710
Bye.

350
00:20:51,990 --> 00:20:53,377
Why are you back so early today?

351
00:21:08,670 --> 00:21:09,300
What's wrong?

352
00:21:11,466 --> 00:21:13,430
Chen Huan'er fainted
due to gastroenteritis.

353
00:21:14,266 --> 00:21:15,780
Tian Chi sent her to the hospital.

354
00:21:16,710 --> 00:21:17,780
Why were they together?

355
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:21,150
No.

356
00:21:22,390 --> 00:21:23,390
I'm really worried.

357
00:21:24,177 --> 00:21:25,511
I have to go back to see her.

358
00:21:26,190 --> 00:21:28,820
Isn't your decision-making meeting
the day after tomorrow?

359
00:21:28,820 --> 00:21:29,733
Are you going back now?

360
00:21:29,755 --> 00:21:30,340
Chen Huan'er

361
00:21:30,340 --> 00:21:31,430
needs me the most right now.

362
00:21:31,511 --> 00:21:32,733
I have to go back to see her.

363
00:21:34,260 --> 00:21:34,780
Well...

364
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:36,200
It's late, and there's no train.

365
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:37,600
How are you going to go back?

366
00:21:39,577 --> 00:21:40,600
Driving license.

367
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:42,230
I'll rent a car back.

368
00:21:43,820 --> 00:21:44,910
Okay, go ahead.

369
00:21:45,088 --> 00:21:46,200
You have my support.

370
00:21:47,020 --> 00:21:47,540
I'll go now.

371
00:21:48,950 --> 00:21:49,630
Take your time.

372
00:21:52,300 --> 00:21:53,340
Take your time.

373
00:22:05,190 --> 00:22:05,910
Press it.

374
00:22:06,670 --> 00:22:07,300
Thank you.

375
00:22:25,740 --> 00:22:26,190
Huan'er.

376
00:22:27,910 --> 00:22:28,710
Tian Chi.

377
00:22:28,990 --> 00:22:30,300
Why are you still here?

378
00:22:30,710 --> 00:22:32,580
I'm worried about you being here alone.

379
00:22:33,111 --> 00:22:34,150
Let me send you back.

380
00:22:34,740 --> 00:22:36,260
I feel much better now.

381
00:22:36,533 --> 00:22:37,400
I can walk on my own.

382
00:22:38,470 --> 00:22:39,100
Let's go.

383
00:22:53,150 --> 00:22:53,710
We're here.

384
00:22:59,133 --> 00:23:00,430
Sorry for bothering you today.

385
00:23:00,820 --> 00:23:01,950
I'll go upstairs first.

386
00:23:02,300 --> 00:23:02,780
Okay.

387
00:23:02,888 --> 00:23:04,266
If you don't feel well again,

388
00:23:04,600 --> 00:23:05,390
remember to tell me.

389
00:23:41,911 --> 00:23:43,755
Thank you
for taking care of my girlfriend.

390
00:23:44,710 --> 00:23:45,870
Sorry to bother you.

391
00:23:48,300 --> 00:23:49,230
Huan'er is my junior.

392
00:23:49,710 --> 00:23:50,990
It's my job to take care of her.

393
00:23:53,500 --> 00:23:55,430
I will take good care of Chen Huan'er.

394
00:23:56,780 --> 00:23:58,340
Next time this happens,

395
00:23:59,430 --> 00:24:00,630
you don't need to worry.

396
00:24:02,020 --> 00:24:02,670
Are you sure?

397
00:24:04,390 --> 00:24:05,060
If Chen Huan'er

398
00:24:05,100 --> 00:24:06,300
faints in front of me again,

399
00:24:07,340 --> 00:24:08,430
you want me to ignore her?

400
00:24:16,020 --> 00:24:16,780
Jing Xichi.

401
00:24:17,580 --> 00:24:19,020
If you really love Chen Huan'er,

402
00:24:19,866 --> 00:24:21,955
how come you didn't even know
she was sick?

403
00:24:25,230 --> 00:24:26,470
You weren't by her side

404
00:24:26,500 --> 00:24:27,933
during her most difficult times.

405
00:24:29,540 --> 00:24:30,230
You have no right

406
00:24:30,260 --> 00:24:31,955
to stop others from being nice to her.

407
00:24:57,500 --> 00:24:58,540
Hello? Senior Gao.

408
00:24:58,820 --> 00:24:59,390
What's wrong?

409
00:24:59,822 --> 00:25:01,020
Hurry and pack your things.

410
00:25:01,111 --> 00:25:02,555
Follow me to Tonglin City tomorrow

411
00:25:02,555 --> 00:25:04,480
for a growth survey
of medicinal plants in the wild.

412
00:25:04,488 --> 00:25:06,666
We'll be staying over,
so bring some change of clothes.

413
00:25:07,230 --> 00:25:08,630
Why so sudden?

414
00:25:09,780 --> 00:25:11,190
Can I not go first?

415
00:25:11,390 --> 00:25:11,820
No.

416
00:25:11,955 --> 00:25:12,870
It's been arranged.

417
00:25:13,060 --> 00:25:14,230
Here's the thing, Senior Gao.

418
00:25:14,910 --> 00:25:16,300
I just got back from the hospital.

419
00:25:16,430 --> 00:25:17,710
I'm not feeling well.

420
00:25:18,300 --> 00:25:19,630
Can I go in two days?

421
00:25:20,470 --> 00:25:21,260
Our experiment

422
00:25:21,288 --> 00:25:23,377
can't be postponed
just because you want to rest.

423
00:25:23,500 --> 00:25:23,950
Senior Gao.

424
00:25:23,990 --> 00:25:25,390
What do you mean by that?

425
00:25:25,740 --> 00:25:26,670
Even if it's delayed,

426
00:25:26,670 --> 00:25:27,230
it's because

427
00:25:27,300 --> 00:25:28,260
you didn't plan

428
00:25:28,390 --> 00:25:29,580
and notify in advance.

429
00:25:29,820 --> 00:25:31,020
Fine. Chen Huan'er.

430
00:25:31,088 --> 00:25:32,390
If you really don't want to go,

431
00:25:32,540 --> 00:25:33,430
I'll find someone else.

432
00:25:33,540 --> 00:25:34,670
But I'm not sure

433
00:25:34,670 --> 00:25:36,600
whether you can
get the credit for this project.

434
00:25:36,630 --> 00:25:37,340
No.

435
00:25:38,155 --> 00:25:39,733
I did everything I should have done

436
00:25:39,777 --> 00:25:41,880
and things I shouldn't have done
in this experiment.

437
00:25:41,888 --> 00:25:43,060
Who are you to deny my credit?

438
00:25:43,060 --> 00:25:45,311
Just because I'm the person in charge
of this project.

439
00:25:52,470 --> 00:25:53,060
Okay.

440
00:25:53,710 --> 00:25:54,470
Got it.

441
00:26:03,066 --> 00:26:03,933
(I'm downstairs.)

442
00:26:17,190 --> 00:26:18,340
Why are you here?

443
00:26:19,430 --> 00:26:20,670
When did you come?

444
00:26:21,540 --> 00:26:22,230
You're sick.

445
00:26:22,260 --> 00:26:23,755
I want to come back to see you.

446
00:26:28,430 --> 00:26:29,340
How are you?

447
00:26:29,777 --> 00:26:30,780
Still feeling unwell?

448
00:26:31,540 --> 00:26:32,500
I'm fine now.

449
00:26:34,540 --> 00:26:35,190
By the way,

450
00:26:35,950 --> 00:26:37,580
how's your proposal going?

451
00:26:38,555 --> 00:26:39,870
I haven't finished writing it yet.

452
00:26:41,870 --> 00:26:42,260
Well...

453
00:26:42,430 --> 00:26:44,060
Why don't you hurry back to work?

454
00:26:47,222 --> 00:26:48,190
So you don't want me

455
00:26:48,190 --> 00:26:49,244
to come back and see you?

456
00:26:49,630 --> 00:26:50,390
No.

457
00:26:50,390 --> 00:26:51,670
That's not what I meant.

458
00:26:52,190 --> 00:26:53,100
What I mean

459
00:26:53,100 --> 00:26:54,550
is that I don't want you to miss work

460
00:26:54,555 --> 00:26:55,377
because of me.

461
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:56,740
Chen Huan'er.

462
00:26:58,820 --> 00:27:00,150
I don't want to be

463
00:27:00,177 --> 00:27:01,888
the last one to know that you're sick.

464
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:04,955
I don't want Tian Chi to be the one
to take you to the hospital

465
00:27:04,955 --> 00:27:06,300
and accompany you back to the dorm

466
00:27:06,390 --> 00:27:07,300
instead of me.

467
00:27:09,470 --> 00:27:11,710
I didn't let him send me.

468
00:27:12,150 --> 00:27:14,190
He was waiting at the hospital.

469
00:27:18,470 --> 00:27:19,630
What do you mean by that?

470
00:27:20,580 --> 00:27:21,580
You don't trust me?

471
00:27:26,060 --> 00:27:27,390
I trust you.

472
00:27:27,488 --> 00:27:28,740
I think you just don't trust me.

473
00:27:28,777 --> 00:27:30,044
What are you agitated about?

474
00:27:30,088 --> 00:27:31,060
I'm not agitated.

475
00:27:31,430 --> 00:27:32,910
Didn't you say it yourself?

476
00:27:34,244 --> 00:27:35,555
If it weren't for Tian Chi,

477
00:27:35,555 --> 00:27:36,377
would you have come?

478
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:37,444
I'll come, of course.

479
00:27:38,311 --> 00:27:40,230
With you being so busy,
will you usually come?

480
00:27:40,260 --> 00:27:41,222
When I said I miss you,

481
00:27:41,266 --> 00:27:41,866
did you come?

482
00:27:41,888 --> 00:27:43,020
So do you think I came back

483
00:27:43,020 --> 00:27:43,933
because of Tian Chi?

484
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:44,577
Yes!

485
00:27:51,870 --> 00:27:53,150
Do you know we haven't

486
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:54,910
had a good talk for a long time?

487
00:27:59,540 --> 00:28:01,020
I also don't want

488
00:28:01,500 --> 00:28:03,060
to have to see your updates

489
00:28:03,100 --> 00:28:04,511
through Fu Ying's social media.

490
00:28:07,230 --> 00:28:07,910
Chen Huan'er.

491
00:28:08,780 --> 00:28:10,060
I've tried very hard.

492
00:28:10,580 --> 00:28:12,066
I'm under great pressure every day

493
00:28:12,066 --> 00:28:13,060
just to finish it quickly

494
00:28:13,060 --> 00:28:14,066
and come back to see you.

495
00:28:14,088 --> 00:28:14,777
And then what?

496
00:28:14,820 --> 00:28:15,710
As soon as I came back,

497
00:28:15,710 --> 00:28:17,488
I saw Tian Chi
sending you back to the dorm!

498
00:28:18,710 --> 00:28:19,670
I've tried very hard

499
00:28:19,780 --> 00:28:21,020
to control my emotions.

500
00:28:21,390 --> 00:28:21,990
And then what?

501
00:28:22,340 --> 00:28:23,580
When I came back

502
00:28:23,780 --> 00:28:24,500
and we met,

503
00:28:24,577 --> 00:28:26,466
the first thing you said
was to let me leave!

504
00:28:26,710 --> 00:28:28,340
That's not what I meant!

505
00:28:29,740 --> 00:28:31,190
Can you be more mature?

506
00:28:31,230 --> 00:28:32,260
Jing Xichi.

507
00:28:33,444 --> 00:28:35,190
Are you the only one
who's tired every day?

508
00:28:35,230 --> 00:28:36,630
I'm tired too.

509
00:28:39,260 --> 00:28:40,300
I attend classes

510
00:28:40,688 --> 00:28:42,311
and do experiments every day.

511
00:28:42,340 --> 00:28:44,622
I also have to go to the mountains
for research tomorrow.

512
00:28:44,710 --> 00:28:46,190
I'm really tired.

513
00:29:00,990 --> 00:29:01,820
Answer it.

514
00:29:11,630 --> 00:29:12,150
Hello?

515
00:29:12,990 --> 00:29:14,100
We found Light Messenger.

516
00:29:14,230 --> 00:29:15,150
They're in Wu'an.

517
00:29:16,670 --> 00:29:17,780
Send me the address.

518
00:29:18,060 --> 00:29:18,820
I'll go find them.

519
00:29:19,230 --> 00:29:20,580
Okay, I'll send you the address.

520
00:29:20,670 --> 00:29:21,230
Alright.

521
00:29:21,670 --> 00:29:22,260
Bye.

522
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:37,340
Huan'er.

523
00:29:38,150 --> 00:29:39,670
I don't want to argue with you.

524
00:29:42,300 --> 00:29:43,390
You should hurry back.

525
00:29:44,444 --> 00:29:45,780
I know that Yangwu's project

526
00:29:45,820 --> 00:29:46,950
is important to you.

527
00:29:48,740 --> 00:29:50,190
Don't delay your work because of me.

528
00:29:53,740 --> 00:29:54,950
I'll go back to pack my things.

529
00:30:15,420 --> 00:30:21,180
♪You're silent in the midst of the lies♪

530
00:30:22,780 --> 00:30:28,540
♪You're also indifferent
to tortuous speculation♪

531
00:30:30,220 --> 00:30:36,060
♪After going through
the story's separations and reunions♪

532
00:30:37,620 --> 00:30:42,620
♪Deprived of regret♪

533
00:30:42,860 --> 00:30:46,260
♪You obviously miss me too♪

534
00:30:46,380 --> 00:30:49,581
♪Why didn't you tell me?♪

535
00:30:51,060 --> 00:30:54,100
♪Gentleness descends from the eyes♪

536
00:30:54,620 --> 00:30:57,540
♪Wrapping up time with me♪

537
00:30:57,540 --> 00:31:01,180
♪You obviously love me too♪

538
00:31:01,180 --> 00:31:05,420
♪Don't miss it again♪

539
00:31:05,620 --> 00:31:09,180
♪Gather roses and fireworks♪

540
00:31:09,460 --> 00:31:20,900
♪I'll watch the sun rise
and the moon set with you♪

541
00:31:41,390 --> 00:31:42,150
Excuse me.

542
00:31:42,470 --> 00:31:43,740
Are you Light Messenger?

543
00:31:47,910 --> 00:31:48,540
Hello?

544
00:31:54,340 --> 00:31:54,910
Hello.

545
00:31:57,340 --> 00:31:58,710
Light Messenger?

546
00:32:00,950 --> 00:32:01,470
Hello.

547
00:32:01,780 --> 00:32:02,710
My name is Jing Xichi.

548
00:32:02,780 --> 00:32:03,870
The founder of Yangwu.

549
00:32:04,780 --> 00:32:05,300
Sorry

550
00:32:05,430 --> 00:32:06,020
to bother you.

551
00:32:06,670 --> 00:32:07,230
My colleague

552
00:32:07,260 --> 00:32:08,260
should have told you

553
00:32:08,260 --> 00:32:09,060
why I'm here, right?

554
00:32:12,020 --> 00:32:14,060
It's mainly because

555
00:32:14,066 --> 00:32:15,910
Yangwu encountered
some difficulties recently.

556
00:32:16,155 --> 00:32:17,311
We're facing transformation.

557
00:32:17,580 --> 00:32:19,340
You've been a regular user
of our website.

558
00:32:19,780 --> 00:32:20,950
Among all users,

559
00:32:21,020 --> 00:32:21,780
your login rate

560
00:32:21,910 --> 00:32:22,820
and activity level

561
00:32:22,910 --> 00:32:23,990
have always been very high.

562
00:32:24,630 --> 00:32:25,670
That's why I want to see

563
00:32:25,870 --> 00:32:26,390
if you

564
00:32:26,430 --> 00:32:27,555
can give us any advice.

565
00:32:28,870 --> 00:32:29,670
Actually,

566
00:32:30,740 --> 00:32:32,190
I want to see you too.

567
00:32:33,780 --> 00:32:34,580
Meet me?

568
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:37,190
Why?

569
00:32:38,150 --> 00:32:39,300
I want to thank you.

570
00:32:43,340 --> 00:32:44,500
I'm

571
00:32:44,910 --> 00:32:45,540
not very good

572
00:32:45,580 --> 00:32:46,580
at dealing with others.

573
00:32:47,540 --> 00:32:49,950
I used to stay at home every day.

574
00:32:50,288 --> 00:32:51,390
I'm not talkative either.

575
00:32:51,533 --> 00:32:52,540
I'm either reading a book

576
00:32:52,540 --> 00:32:54,300
or looking at the stars
with a telescope.

577
