593
00:33:30,950 --> 00:33:31,820
It made me realize

594
00:33:32,500 --> 00:33:33,710
that as long as each star

595
00:33:33,740 --> 00:33:34,780
illuminates one other,

596
00:33:34,844 --> 00:33:36,644
they can gather
into the brightest galaxy

597
00:33:36,644 --> 00:33:37,540
in the dark night.

