to do research.

621
00:34:54,870 --> 00:34:55,620
Tonglin Village?

622
00:35:01,933 --> 00:35:03,555
(Soil Fertilizer
Nutrient Level Rapid Tester)

623
00:35:03,911 --> 00:35:05,177
By the way, Chen Huan'er,

624
00:35:06,020 --> 00:35:07,222
