625
00:35:16,950 --> 00:35:17,500
Three,

626
00:35:17,870 --> 00:35:18,350
two,

627
00:35:18,790 --> 00:35:19,430
one.

628
00:35:20,750 --> 00:35:21,270
All done.

629
00:35:21,700 --> 00:35:22,180
Okay.

630
00:35:22,540 --> 00:35:23,270
Take a look.

631
00:35:25,910 --> 00:35:26,620
Not bad.

632
00:35:27,830 --> 00:35:28,100
Okay.

633
00:35:28,220 --> 00:35:29,140
