639
00:35:39,100 --> 00:35:39,540
Okay?

640
00:35:39,990 --> 00:35:40,270
Lu.

641
00:35:40,270 --> 00:35:40,620
No...

642
00:35:40,660 --> 00:35:41,500
- Let's go.
- Okay.

643
00:35:59,140 --> 00:35:59,950
Hello? Jing.

644
00:36:00,977 --> 00:36:02,600
I have Yangwu's proposal
for the meeting,

645
00:36:02,660 --> 00:36:03,660
but I can't go back.

646
00:36:03,790 --> 00:36:05,111
Go to the meeting with Zhou Ye.

647
00:36:05,390 --> 00:36:06,020
Me?

648
00:36:06,310 --> 00:36:07,140
Where did you go?

649
00:36:07,733 --> 00:36:09,888
Something happened to Huan'er.
I'm going to find her.

650
00:36:09,990 --> 00:36:11,580
But you're the one in charge of Yangwu.

651
00:36:11,644 --> 00:36:13,466
Is it appropriate
for me to take your place?

652
00:36:13,533 --> 00:36:14,311
It's okay.

653
00:36:14,311 --> 00:36:15,220
We're all a team.

654
00:36:15,910 --> 00:36:17,990
Besides, you've done no less for Yangwu
than I have.

655
00:36:18,288 --> 00:36:19,270
If it weren't for you,

656
00:36:19,300 --> 00:36:20,777
Yangwu wouldn't be where it is today.

657
00:36:21,620 --> 00:36:22,580
What should I say then?

658
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:03,755
It's raining so hard,

659
00:37:03,777 --> 00:37:05,510
but you're going up
for scientific research?

660
00:37:05,533 --> 00:37:06,580
It's too dangerous.

661
00:37:07,470 --> 00:37:09,060
The weather was good just now.

662
00:37:09,100 --> 00:37:11,577
Who knew the weather on this mountain
would change so quickly?

663
00:37:11,580 --> 00:37:12,470
Yeah.

664
00:37:13,180 --> 00:37:14,700
The mountains around Tonglin Village

665
00:37:14,866 --> 00:37:15,620
are too dangerous.

666
00:37:16,430 --> 00:37:18,060
There was a wildfire here
many years ago.

667
00:37:18,430 --> 00:37:19,470
A firefighter

668
00:37:19,511 --> 00:37:20,700
was trapped in the mountains

669
00:37:21,310 --> 00:37:22,180
and never came out.

670
00:37:23,270 --> 00:37:24,060
He never came out?

671
00:37:44,950 --> 00:37:45,580
Who is it?

672
00:37:46,733 --> 00:37:47,844
Where's Chen Huan'er?

673
00:37:47,977 --> 00:37:49,769
She went up the mountain
to collect samples.

674
00:37:49,770 --> 00:37:50,750
No news of her after that.

675
00:37:50,755 --> 00:37:51,622
I can't reach her.

676
00:37:51,622 --> 00:37:52,750
Letting her go alone today?

677
00:37:52,750 --> 00:37:54,020
The weather was fine this morning.

678
00:37:54,020 --> 00:37:55,690
Who knew
it would suddenly start to rain?

679
00:37:55,711 --> 00:37:56,533
Don't worry.

680
00:37:56,555 --> 00:37:58,311
Maybe her phone
just doesn't have a signal.

681
00:37:58,333 --> 00:37:59,377
Do you even have a heart?

682
00:37:59,910 --> 00:38:00,350
You...

683
00:38:01,390 --> 00:38:01,700
You...

684
00:38:04,220 --> 00:38:05,060
Jerk.

685
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:11,580
Chen Huan'er!

686
00:38:14,270 --> 00:38:15,140
Chen Huan'er!

687
00:38:17,310 --> 00:38:18,140
Chen Huan'er!

688
00:38:19,620 --> 00:38:20,540
Chen Huan'er!

689
00:38:22,020 --> 00:38:22,870
Chen Huan'er!

690
00:39:06,140 --> 00:39:07,350
(Retreat first.)

691
00:39:08,100 --> 00:39:08,660
(Retreat.)

692
00:39:10,140 --> 00:39:10,790
(Hurry up!)

693
00:39:11,060 --> 00:39:11,830
(Catch up.)

694
00:39:12,540 --> 00:39:13,220
(Hurry.)

695
00:39:18,140 --> 00:39:19,020
(Hurry and retreat!)

696
00:39:41,060 --> 00:39:41,700
(Xichi.)

697
00:39:42,430 --> 00:39:42,990
(Xichi.)

698
00:39:44,022 --> 00:39:45,830
(Thank you for your hard work
over the years.)

699
00:39:47,350 --> 00:39:49,750
(You're really a grown-up now.)

700
00:40:55,910 --> 00:40:56,750
Drink something hot.

701
00:40:56,830 --> 00:40:57,620
Warm yourself up.

702
00:40:58,830 --> 00:40:59,500
Thank you.

703
00:41:00,870 --> 00:41:01,830
There's no signal here.

704
00:41:01,870 --> 00:41:02,830
I just tried.

705
00:41:04,020 --> 00:41:06,200
It's late now. It's dangerous
to descend the mountain.

706
00:41:06,200 --> 00:41:07,488
Let's wait till dawn.

707
00:41:13,222 --> 00:41:14,220
What is this place?

708
00:41:16,180 --> 00:41:17,660
This is our supply stop

709
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:18,660
for sample collection.

710
00:41:21,390 --> 00:41:22,870
Why did you come here suddenly?

711
00:41:24,555 --> 00:41:26,133
I couldn't get in touch with you.

712
00:41:27,020 --> 00:41:28,020
So I called Tian Chi.

713
00:41:29,310 --> 00:41:30,750
He said you went to Tonglin Village.

714
00:41:31,540 --> 00:41:32,470
I heard

715
00:41:32,688 --> 00:41:34,244
and couldn't care about anything else.

716
00:41:35,430 --> 00:41:36,270
Are you okay?

717
00:41:36,711 --> 00:41:37,700
You're not hurt, are you?

718
00:41:39,500 --> 00:41:40,430
I'm fine.

719
00:41:43,270 --> 00:41:44,270
What happened to you

720
00:41:46,390 --> 00:41:46,950
just now?

721
00:41:51,660 --> 00:41:52,220
I'm fine.

722
00:41:58,990 --> 00:41:59,790
Wait here.

723
00:42:09,430 --> 00:42:10,060
Take this.

724
00:42:17,020 --> 00:42:17,950
What's this?

725
00:42:19,750 --> 00:42:21,540
This is the vegetation soil
after the fire.

726
00:42:22,870 --> 00:42:23,790
After the fire,

727
00:42:24,220 --> 00:42:25,540
the vegetation restoration period

728
00:42:25,580 --> 00:42:27,000
can be as short as a dozen years

729
00:42:27,350 --> 00:42:28,790
or as long as several decades.

730
00:42:29,470 --> 00:42:31,060
It's a very long process,

731
00:42:32,060 --> 00:42:32,910
but

732
00:42:33,060 --> 00:42:34,500
it continues to grow

733
00:42:34,790 --> 00:42:36,310
even if it looks barren.

734
00:42:36,910 --> 00:42:37,990
One day,

735
00:42:38,990 --> 00:42:40,220
it will return

736
00:42:40,222 --> 00:42:41,660
to its original lush appearance.

737
00:42:46,270 --> 00:42:46,870
Huan'er.

738
00:42:49,310 --> 00:42:50,020
Sorry.

739
00:42:52,060 --> 00:42:53,060
I shouldn't have

740
00:42:54,844 --> 00:42:56,180
lost my temper with you yesterday.

741
00:42:58,700 --> 00:42:59,540
It's all over now.

742
00:43:00,622 --> 00:43:02,022
Let's not mention it anymore.

743
00:43:12,220 --> 00:43:13,180
This is nice.

744
00:43:14,350 --> 00:43:15,500
It seems like

745
00:43:15,870 --> 00:43:17,700
we haven't sat together
quietly like this

746
00:43:18,100 --> 00:43:19,990
for a long time.

747
00:43:24,060 --> 00:43:25,220
In these past few days,

748
00:43:26,430 --> 00:43:27,620
I've been thinking

749
00:43:29,660 --> 00:43:31,060
whether my decision to leave Wu'an

750
00:43:31,140 --> 00:43:32,430
for Jing City

751
00:43:34,020 --> 00:43:35,020
was right or wrong.

752
00:43:39,060 --> 00:43:40,310
It's true

753
00:43:41,444 --> 00:43:42,990
that I've been busy this month,

754
00:43:44,990 --> 00:43:46,430
but it's also true

755
00:43:48,333 --> 00:43:49,955
that my heart feels empty.

756
00:43:52,790 --> 00:43:54,220
When I was in Wu'an,

757
00:43:55,790 --> 00:43:57,620
my favorite thing of the day

758
00:43:58,533 --> 00:44:00,140
was to take the subway for half an hour

759
00:44:02,390 --> 00:44:03,580
at 6:30 PM

760
00:44:04,430 --> 00:44:05,790
and change buses three times

761
00:44:07,660 --> 00:44:09,310
so that I could go across the city

762
00:44:09,870 --> 00:44:10,750
to see you.

763
00:44:13,790 --> 00:44:15,140
But after arriving in Jing City,

764
00:44:17,700 --> 00:44:18,910
there's no bus

765
00:44:20,470 --> 00:44:21,470
or subway

766
00:44:24,950 --> 00:44:26,350
that can take me to you.

767
00:44:39,660 --> 00:44:40,910
I feel the same way.

768
00:44:43,220 --> 00:44:44,830
I've already regarded

769
00:44:44,910 --> 00:44:46,270
Wu'an as my other home.

770
00:44:48,100 --> 00:44:49,700
But since you left,

771
00:44:51,180 --> 00:44:52,350
I just feel

772
00:44:52,990 --> 00:44:54,350
that even the most familiar places

773
00:44:56,220 --> 00:44:57,500
have become unfamiliar.

774
00:45:02,350 --> 00:45:03,180
Chen Huan'er.

775
00:45:05,620 --> 00:45:06,870
Will you regret

776
00:45:09,060 --> 00:45:09,950
being with me?

777
00:45:12,750 --> 00:45:14,470
Have you lost your mind?

778
00:45:17,470 --> 00:45:18,470
Do you know

779
00:45:18,830 --> 00:45:21,060
why I'm called Chen Huan'er?

780
00:45:23,422 --> 00:45:25,733
Because I was always hospitalized
when I was a kid.

781
00:45:25,866 --> 00:45:27,540
The nurses wouldn't
call patients' names.

782
00:45:27,660 --> 00:45:30,180
They only called the patient in bed 3

783
00:45:30,470 --> 00:45:31,620
or the patient in bed 5.

784
00:45:32,390 --> 00:45:33,500
Whenever my mom

785
00:45:33,580 --> 00:45:34,870
heard these words,

786
00:45:35,140 --> 00:45:36,430
she would be frightened.

787
00:45:37,790 --> 00:45:38,830
But my mom said

788
00:45:39,620 --> 00:45:40,660
since we're stuck with it,

789
00:45:41,390 --> 00:45:42,830
we'll try to turn the bad

790
00:45:43,310 --> 00:45:44,350
into good.

791
00:45:46,100 --> 00:45:46,950
That's why

792
00:45:48,100 --> 00:45:49,390
those words

793
00:45:49,430 --> 00:45:51,400
became my name.
[*Patient sounds like Huan'er in Chinese]

794
00:45:51,620 --> 00:45:52,990
She hopes I can

795
00:45:53,310 --> 00:45:54,660
grow up happily

796
00:45:54,830 --> 00:45:56,310
amidst laughter and joy.

797
00:45:58,955 --> 00:46:00,977
I've been thinking about it
over the years.

798
00:46:01,950 --> 00:46:02,870
Am I happy?

799
00:46:06,100 --> 00:46:07,310
I didn't know before,

800
00:46:09,140 --> 00:46:10,500
but now I know.

801
00:46:12,620 --> 00:46:13,660
I'm quite happy.

802
00:46:16,750 --> 00:46:18,470
Especially after meeting you.

803
00:46:23,220 --> 00:46:25,020
You never reject

804
00:46:25,220 --> 00:46:27,270
my weird ideas

805
00:46:29,500 --> 00:46:30,350
and always

806
00:46:30,390 --> 00:46:31,660
support me silently behind me.

807
00:46:33,620 --> 00:46:35,310
(Maybe you're a little unreliable)

808
00:46:36,750 --> 00:46:38,870
(in the eyes of outsiders.)

809
00:46:41,140 --> 00:46:42,350
(But in my eyes,)

810
00:46:43,350 --> 00:46:44,910
(your unreliability)

811
00:46:46,580 --> 00:46:48,140
(is exactly what I need.)

812
00:46:53,830 --> 00:46:54,660
That's why

813
00:46:56,390 --> 00:46:58,750
I'm grateful to have met you.

814
00:47:02,790 --> 00:47:04,620
I also cherish our relationship.

815
00:47:08,580 --> 00:47:09,500
I don't regret it.

816
00:47:11,790 --> 00:47:12,580
Chen Huan'er.

817
00:47:15,910 --> 00:47:16,830
I love you.

818
00:47:20,540 --> 00:47:22,310
Why so sentimental?

819
00:47:28,020 --> 00:47:29,060
Jing Xichi.

820
00:47:33,020 --> 00:47:34,140
I love you too.

821
00:48:10,880 --> 00:48:16,050
♪Fallen leaves flutter past your gaze♪

822
00:48:17,840 --> 00:48:22,920
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

823
00:48:24,690 --> 00:48:30,040
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

824
00:48:30,350 --> 00:48:35,840
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

825
00:48:38,430 --> 00:48:43,450
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

826
00:48:45,240 --> 00:48:50,480
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

827
00:48:52,080 --> 00:48:57,500
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

828
00:48:57,960 --> 00:49:03,460
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

829
00:49:04,660 --> 00:49:08,620
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

830
00:49:08,620 --> 00:49:13,610
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

831
00:49:13,740 --> 00:49:17,170
♪And full of life♪

832
00:49:18,460 --> 00:49:21,920
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

833
00:49:21,920 --> 00:49:27,030
♪Would regrets rewrite
where we'd gone wrong?♪

834
00:49:27,290 --> 00:49:31,680
♪And let me be there with you
at the end of the story♪

835
00:49:32,180 --> 00:49:36,080
♪Watching your silhouette from behind♪

836
00:49:36,080 --> 00:49:41,020
♪My footsteps slow, we were too young♪

837
00:49:41,020 --> 00:49:43,810
♪To know right from wrong♪

838
00:49:45,720 --> 00:49:49,250
♪Your sweat-kissed face
I hold in my memory♪

839
00:49:49,250 --> 00:49:52,500
♪Glows as bright as ever♪

840
00:49:52,660 --> 00:49:58,420
♪I hope one day we'll meet again♪

841
00:49:58,840 --> 00:50:03,440
♪At just the right time♪

